snippet.title: Skader - ice-skating in VR - Early Demo
snippet.description:
SKADER is a sci-fi MOBA game with unique locomotion, where you can play with or against your friends by ice-skating around sophisticated features and leaving behind trails to catch your opponents. I'm also glad to announce that I'm starting a closed beta-test group for a limited number of players. Every active beta-testers will get a free copy of the game once  released. Please join the game Discord server to stay tuned for updates or join the beta group, chat with developers and share your ideas:

https://discord.gg/abb4D8p3
